{"chunk_id": "mcf_chunk_0010", "doc_id": "mcf", "chunk_index": 10, "content": "A: Yes. You may opt to become a deferred member of the plan after leaving the Foundation. Your savings will continue to accrue interest and can be accessed at a later date. The same withdrawal process applies. Please contact the Specialised Services team to initiate the withdrawal when ready.", "chunk_type": "text", "page_refs": [1], "bounding_box": {"x0": 70.91999849999999, "y0": 495.14047989381214, "x1": 557.695745780253, "y1": 526.9578238500001, "page": 1}, "content_hash": "78a3eb418e97db22026255070c5810e678db8a8e01f7af39661f85e95f4f7f58", "parent_section": "Q: Can we leave the contributions as savings for future use?", "parent_section_page": 1, "token_count": 73, "relationships": [], "table_data": null, "figure_caption": null, "strategy_used": "B"}
