{"chunk_id": "mcf_chunk_0021", "doc_id": "mcf", "chunk_index": 21, "content": " After  the  final  pension  contribution  is  received  (last  payroll  run),  Alex  Forbes  issues  leaving  service options paperwork directly to the employee. The employee completes it (including bank details).", "chunk_type": "text", "page_refs": [1], "bounding_box": {"x0": 88.91999849999999, "y0": 312.74049339381213, "x1": 557.7559435820873, "y1": 333.03782609999996, "page": 1}, "content_hash": "6418fdfc8b6cded0ff0d65d2f7e495609a89891676d99be22f373a7bc2873c34", "parent_section": "B. ISP Withdrawal Process", "parent_section_page": 1, "token_count": 53, "relationships": [], "table_data": null, "figure_caption": null, "strategy_used": "B"}
{"chunk_id": "mcf_chunk_0022", "doc_id": "mcf", "chunk_index": 22, "content": " After  all  documents  are  submitted  and  Trustee  approval  is  received,  Alex  Forbes  arranges  the disinvestment of funds.", "chunk_type": "text", "page_refs": [1], "bounding_box": {"x0": 88.91999849999999, "y0": 279.74049339381213, "x1": 557.7872036692701, "y1": 300.03782609999996, "page": 1}, "content_hash": "78cca6ba3e6372db9cf17d4e8afbcbf8ec6ff90e8e2b6f54adb7213bcfc96668", "parent_section": "B. ISP Withdrawal Process", "parent_section_page": 1, "token_count": 32, "relationships": [], "table_data": null, "figure_caption": null, "strategy_used": "B"}
