{"chunk_id": "mcf_chunk_0026", "doc_id": "mcf", "chunk_index": 26, "content": "A: Medical cover ends on the last day of employment for the principal member.", "chunk_type": "text", "page_refs": [1], "bounding_box": {"x0": 70.91999849999999, "y0": 202.34048439381218, "x1": 421.3784120401946, "y1": 211.11782760000006, "page": 1}, "content_hash": "1e9e948557c13e07646001da650f4a8e933604fb035a4d2973cc6c8db83ca6aa", "parent_section": "Q: When does medical cover end after leaving the Foundation?", "parent_section_page": 1, "token_count": 19, "relationships": [], "table_data": null, "figure_caption": null, "strategy_used": "B"}
{"chunk_id": "mcf_chunk_0027", "doc_id": "mcf", "chunk_index": 27, "content": "Q: Can medical cover be extended beyond the last day of employment?", "chunk_type": "heading", "page_refs": [1], "bounding_box": {"x0": 70.91999849999999, "y0": 179.30282390303864, "x1": 412.91605065525346, "y1": 188.06790824999996, "page": 1}, "content_hash": "f49b29397ebbaeff75397cc631f0083b3c786bfdebb59da73fbc4fcab2160d46", "parent_section": "Q: Can medical cover be extended beyond the last day of employment?", "parent_section_page": 1, "token_count": 16, "relationships": [], "table_data": null, "figure_caption": null, "strategy_used": "B"}
{"chunk_id": "mcf_chunk_0028", "doc_id": "mcf", "chunk_index": 28, "content": "A: Yes, but only in exceptional circumstances and with approval by the Director, Total Rewards and Mobility. Even then, the cover may only be extended up to the next renewal date of the group medical plan.", "chunk_type": "text", "page_refs": [1], "bounding_box": {"x0": 70.91999849999999, "y0": 156.38046264381205, "x1": 557.8007875187043, "y1": 176.55781485, "page": 1}, "content_hash": "d0b7f94461e29a461131b26039d83c42e1e6c5355564b6a0052929d51c32dc2e", "parent_section": "Q: Can medical cover be extended beyond the last day of employment?", "parent_section_page": 1, "token_count": 51, "relationships": [], "table_data": null, "figure_caption": null, "strategy_used": "B"}
