{"chunk_id": "mcf_chunk_0033", "doc_id": "mcf", "chunk_index": 33, "content": "A: No. BMW does not provide upfront payments. It operates on a pay-and-claim basis, meaning the expense must have been incurred by the employee in the same year of the claim to be reimbursed.", "chunk_type": "text", "page_refs": [1], "bounding_box": {"x0": 70.91999849999999, "y0": 75.86047314381221, "x1": 557.77574060908, "y1": 96.15780584999993, "page": 1}, "content_hash": "254b38c57ddb1f6c52fedb639b3c3d1f9474062b35071d9d706f4ae2010cee1e", "parent_section": "Q: Can I pay for a course now and claim from BMW later?", "parent_section_page": 1, "token_count": 47, "relationships": [], "table_data": null, "figure_caption": null, "strategy_used": "B"}
